com.ausregistry.jtoolkit2.se

Class NotificationResponse

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ausregistry.jtoolkit2.se.Response
      • com.ausregistry.jtoolkit2.se.DataResponse
        • com.ausregistry.jtoolkit2.se.NotificationResponse
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ContactNotificationResponse, DomainNotificationResponse

    public abstract class NotificationResponse
extends DataResponse
    When offline processing of an action has been completed by the server operator, a message is enqueued for the client who requested the action. The NotificationResponse class models the pending action notification data informing the client of the completion of offline processing. A NotificationResponse is always specific to a particular object mapping, and so a subclass of this models the specific object data - such an object is returned by methods in PollResponse.
    See Also:
    PollRequestCommand, PollResponse, Serialized Form
